1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:42,270
[I Don't Want to Be Friends With You]

3
00:01:42,410 --> 00:01:43,800
Let's take a picture. Hurry
up, come here. Come here.

4
00:01:43,890 --> 00:01:44,770
Hurry up.

5
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,170
[Learned, Inspired, Educated]

6
00:01:48,170 --> 00:01:49,090
Ready.

7
00:01:55,250 --> 00:01:59,240
[Today Is a Very Lucky Day
Fan Shui Shui Treats Us to Chicken. Hey Hey]

8
00:02:24,820 --> 00:02:32,210
[Episode 23]
[Never Separate After Bidding Farewell]

9
00:02:36,970 --> 00:02:38,090
Hua.

10
00:02:39,579 --> 00:02:41,940
Do you think it's our problem?

11
00:02:45,010 --> 00:02:45,890
I don't know.

12
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:50,760
It's not easy to be with someone we like.

13
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:54,000
At last we asked for breaking up.

14
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,320
Are we crazy?

15
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,720
Maybe

16
00:03:00,160 --> 00:03:01,840
we are just this kind of people.

17
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,210
What kind of people are we?

18
00:03:05,530 --> 00:03:07,170
Heartless people.

19
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:11,880
No.

20
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,520
We can't be so sad anymore.

21
00:03:15,660 --> 00:03:16,540
True.

22
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,800
It's not our style.

23
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,810
Let's get something to eat!

24
00:03:21,770 --> 00:03:22,570
Okay.

25
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:23,520
Let's go for dumplings.

26
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:25,680
When will you come back?

27
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,640
I don't know.

28
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:28,640
Maybe in several months.

29
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:30,320
The school will arrange.

30
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,720
Okay.

31
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,430
Go out and have some fun.

32
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,400
It's good.

33
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:37,520
I'll be off then.

34
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,280
She...

35
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,600
If something happens
with the two of them,

36
00:03:44,370 --> 00:03:45,400
call me.

37
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:46,960
Don't worry.

38
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:27,960
[This is for you.]

39
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,160
[You bought it for me?]

40
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,200
[I made it myself.]

41
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:32,560
[It's the first time I make it.]

42
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:34,070
[It might fall apart in the future.]

43
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:35,030
[Impossible.]

44
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,409
[Even if I break it, it won't fall apart.]

45
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:37,680
[That's a deal.]

46
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,930
[If you lose it, we will fall out.]

47
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:40,670
[Don't worry.]

48
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:41,480
[I won't lose it.]

49
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,440
[Let me put it on for you.]

50
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:45,880
[Hua.]

51
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,360
[I like you.]

52
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,640
[We'll be together sooner or later.]

53
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:53,920
[We must be together.]

54
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:57,159
[Then...]

55
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,760
[what if I leave?]

56
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,320
[I'll go find you.]

57
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,520
[No matter where you are,]

58
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,200
[I'll find you.]

59
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,080
[I'm leaving then.]

60
00:05:26,030 --> 00:05:26,910
No.

61
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:27,710
Eat slowly.

62
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,240
Leave some dumplings for me.

63
00:05:29,330 --> 00:05:30,880
I just ate half of them.

64
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:32,710
I said I would have ten plates today.

65
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,680
I don't care. I'm the most disappointed
in a love affair.

66
00:05:35,170 --> 00:05:35,870
I was disappointed, too.

67
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:36,840
The biggest disappointment.

68
00:05:37,250 --> 00:05:38,550
You dumped him.

69
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:40,280
So did you.

70
00:05:41,010 --> 00:05:42,440
It's boring to be in love.

71
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,080
It's a waste of money and energy.

72
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,040
You're right.

73
00:05:46,170 --> 00:05:47,550
We won't be in love anymore.

74
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,600
The two of us can get by.

75
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,870
No. We should be in love
like Wan Wan later.

76
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,120
Change boyfriend once a month.

77
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:52,950
No.

78
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,070
Change boyfriend like mood changes.

79
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,590
Change like these dumplings.

80
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,030
I don't want this one.
It got cold.

81
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,050
I want the next plate.

82
00:05:59,050 --> 00:06:00,480
Okay. The next plate.

83
00:06:05,140 --> 00:06:07,240
[Certificate of Merit]

84
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:09,930
I'm a little reluctant to move out

85
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:13,040
after living here for so long.

86
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:14,840
It doesn't matter.

87
00:06:15,450 --> 00:06:17,040
It's all for the future of our son.

88
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:18,760
I think it will be worth it.

89
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,640
My boy is here.

90
00:07:12,300 --> 00:07:17,170
[Li Qing Tong]

91
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,760
200 yuan more each.

92
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,159
Thank you.

93
00:07:55,250 --> 00:07:56,390
You're welcome.

94
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,320
It's not easy for two girls.

95
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:00,440
Come here again
if you have a chance later on.

96
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,050
We graduated.

97
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,080
You did?

98
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:12,230
All right, don't be so sad.

99
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:14,120
It doesn't mean
we won't meet in the future.

100
00:08:15,050 --> 00:08:16,430
Let's make a deal.

101
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:18,510
We'll visit you in your hometown later.

102
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,440
That's settled.

103
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,400
You must come.

104
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,850
You two are still sad?

105
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:27,960
It's just a break-up. What's the big deal?

106
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,120
There's a long way to go.

107
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:32,080
I'm sure you'll meet
someone better in the future.

108
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,039
Have no regrets.

109
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,880
I'll always be on your side.

110
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,160
The same to you.

111
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,120
Get along well with Da Wang.

112
00:08:53,890 --> 00:08:55,090
Invite me when you get married.

113
00:08:58,520 --> 00:09:00,440
Well, hurry up.

114
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:03,800
Why do you give us lessons
as Miss Lover before leaving?

115
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:06,330
Okay.

116
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:07,560
I'm leaving.

117
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,400
Don't cry.

118
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,640
Are you also leaving today?

119
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,610
Da Wang has already bought the tickets.

120
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:37,600
Then we'll leave after seeing you off.

121
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:45,560
It's okay, just go back.

122
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,560
Remember to come to visit me.

123
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,130
Wish you a safe journey.

124
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,720
Then I'm leaving.

125
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,370
[It's time to say goodbye again.]

126
00:10:09,810 --> 00:10:11,520
[It seems that we have got used to it.]

127
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:13,150
[But this time,]

128
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:15,120
[we say goodbye not only
to the familiar school]

129
00:10:15,210 --> 00:10:16,790
[and familiar classmates,]

130
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:18,480
[but also them.]

131
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:22,040
[I always feel that I'm impersonal.]

132
00:10:22,130 --> 00:10:24,710
[I'm glad I've understood it
at a young age.]

133
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:27,110
[What should be given up
must be given up earlier.]

134
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,680
[It seemed I did it.]

135
00:10:29,170 --> 00:10:29,910
[But,]

136
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,520
[is it correct?]

137
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,840
[I don't know.]

138
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,470
[Maybe if I can choose once more,]

139
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:37,360
[I'll try to be naive.]

140
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,910
[I wouldn't care about the result]

141
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,200
[or the reality.]

142
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:42,960
[I could be with them without
caring about anything.]

143
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:44,720
[But I know]

144
00:10:44,810 --> 00:10:46,680
[I have no chance to choose once more.]

145
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:49,150
[Because the real farewell]

146
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,850
[is coming.]

147
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:58,680
♫ I'm watching you
disappear into the distance ♫

148
00:10:58,770 --> 00:11:03,150
♫ But the memory just won't leave ♫

149
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:05,510
♫ It's like the flower won't bear fruit ♫

150
