♫ The rain and dew are struggling ♫

151
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:10,720
♫ The more reluctant I am ♫

152
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:16,880
♫ The more I miss in my heart ♫

153
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:39,600
♫ Why does the paused love get stranded? ♫

154
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:44,160
♫ My face is covered with tears
when I understand ♫

155
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:49,720
♫ We meet at the right time
but not in the right way ♫

156
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:54,240
♫ We miss after being gone ♫

157
00:11:54,330 --> 00:11:56,470
♫ We were shy at that time ♫

158
