163
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:10,790
♫ The appointment of the aurora ♫

164
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:15,800
♫ You are the light that warms my sight ♫

165
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:21,870
♫ The life over the years
is a blank paper ♫

166
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:26,510
♫ I'm clinging to the time
when I met you at eighteen ♫

167
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:29,150
♫ Time and space are boundless ♫

168
