00:12:49,760 --> 00:12:51,950
♫ The rain and dew are struggling ♫

174
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:55,120
♫ The more reluctant I am ♫

175
00:12:55,880 --> 00:13:01,040
♫ The more I miss in my heart ♫

