00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:14,000
♫ The life over the years
is a blank paper ♫

177
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:18,640
♫ I'm clinging to the time
when I met you at eighteen ♫

178
00:13:18,730 --> 00:13:21,280
♫ Time and space are boundless ♫

179
00:13:21,370 --> 00:13:23,800
♫ The wave ripples ♫

180
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:29,160
♫ Thank you for your wonderful treasure ♫

181
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:34,950
♫ I'm watching you
disappear into the distance ♫

182
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:39,530
♫ But the memory just won't leave ♫

183
00:13:40,850 --> 00:13:41,960
[Wu Zhi Xun.]

184
00:13:43,050 --> 00:13:44,680
[Let's break up.]

185
00:13:48,010 --> 00:13:53,170
♫ The more I miss in my heart ♫

186
00:14:12,330 --> 00:14:13,440
Why did you

187
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:16,640
rent a house on the sixth floor?

188
00:14:16,730 --> 00:14:18,190
I'm exhausted!

189
00:14:18,280 --> 00:14:20,240
It's not bad, okay?

190
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:22,390
Thanks to Mrs Ye

191
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:25,000
we could find a house to rent.

192
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:28,120
Why don't we go back to Tieyuan?

193
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:32,520
Didn't you say you wanted to pursue
your career in a big city?

194
00:14:37,410 --> 00:14:38,610
I'm just complaining.

195
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:54,840
What's the matter?

196
00:14:56,330 --> 00:14:57,210
It's all right.

197
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:59,110
I don't know what's going on these days.

198
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,590
Maybe I didn't rest properly.

199
00:15:00,680 --> 00:15:02,050
I feel like I'm going to vomit
all the time.

200
00:15:02,520 --> 00:15:04,000
Don't tell me you're pregnant.

201
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,640
Pregnant of you...

202
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,440
Just kidding.

203
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,250
I'll go to the bathroom.

204
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:41,600
No way.

205
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:49,040
Hello.

206
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:51,400
May I help you?

207
00:15:56,530 --> 00:15:58,360
Well, is there anything

208
00:15:59,800 --> 00:16:01,920
to check for pregnancy?

209
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:04,800
Yes. Wait a minute, I'll get it for you.

210
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:21,430
Li Qing Tong.

211
00:16:21,520 --> 00:16:23,400
What are you doing
in the bathroom all day?

212
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:32,430
Li Qing Tong.

213
00:16:32,520 --> 00:16:34,050
Come out and help me.

214
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:36,310
Li Qing Tong.

215
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:37,640
Do you hear me?

216
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,210
I'm coming.

217
00:17:18,300 --> 00:17:21,740
[Wu Zhi Xun]

218
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:42,660
[Wu Zhi Xun]

219
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:18,520
Here it goes some good news.

220
00:18:19,360 --> 00:18:20,960
What good news would that be?

221
00:18:22,280 --> 00:18:22,320
Look.

222
00:18:22,320 --> 00:18:23,650
[Health Check-up]

223
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:32,120
The head office informed us
about the physical examination.

224
00:18:32,210 --> 00:18:33,470
As long as we're qualified,

225
00:18:33,560 --> 00:18:35,240
we can join immediately.

226
00:18:40,600 --> 00:18:41,600
What are you still thinking about?

227
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:44,210
Get up early tomorrow and have
a physical examination with me.

228
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:55,880
Li Qing Tong.

229
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:57,000
Are you in there?

230
00:18:59,360 --> 00:19:01,080
I... I have diarrhoea.

231
00:19:01,930 --> 00:19:03,640
Why do you have diarrhoea every day?

232
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:06,120
I don't know.

233
00:19:06,210 --> 00:19:07,800
Maybe I ate something wrong.

234
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:09,990
Would you like some medicine?

235
00:19:10,080 --> 00:19:10,960
No.

236
00:19:27,460 --> 00:19:32,040
[Clinical Laboratory]

237
00:19:32,040 --> 00:19:33,170
Chen Jun He.

238
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:45,190
Where are you going?

239
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:46,240
Jiang Da Fan.

240
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:48,000
Go inside to draw blood.

241
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:52,180
[Color Ultrasonic Room 2]

242
00:20:04,970 --> 00:20:05,710
You.

243
00:20:05,800 --> 00:20:06,880
Why are you here?

244
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:08,880
I'm here for the physical examination.

245
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:10,370
Why are you here?

246
00:20:12,480 --> 00:20:14,000
I just came here for a check-up.

247
00:20:14,080 --> 00:20:15,480
You... you should hurry and go
for the physical examination.

248
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:17,520
[Li Qing Tong.]

249
00:20:17,850 --> 00:20:18,730
[Come in.]

250
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:22,480
[The father should come in, too.]

251
00:20:33,050 --> 00:20:36,530
[Close The Door Behind You]

252
00:20:36,530 --> 00:20:41,700
[People's Hospital]

253
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:58,130
Why are you here alone?

254
00:21:00,330 --> 00:21:01,120
It's none of your business.

255
00:21:01,210 --> 00:21:02,590
Can you just pretend you didn't see me?

256
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:03,600
Where's Wu Zhi Xun?

257
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:07,920
He went to America.

258
00:21:08,840 --> 00:21:10,720
He left you here alone
after such a thing happened?

259
00:21:13,600 --> 00:21:14,680
We've broken up.

260
00:21:18,600 --> 00:21:19,570
Broken up?

261
00:21:20,450 --> 00:21:22,600
You are pregnant. How can you
break up according to your mood?

262
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:24,470
Can you just mind your business?

263
00:21:24,560 --> 00:21:25,440
I have to go.

264
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:28,930
Now that I know it, I can't ignore it.

265
00:21:38,520 --> 00:21:40,490
So you're going to keep it from him?

266
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:45,960
I put forward the break-up first.

267
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,640
It's not easy for him to go to America.

268
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:50,800
I don't want to hold him back.

269
00:21:51,280 --> 00:21:52,600
But what about the baby?

270
00:21:53,690 --> 00:21:55,920
You're going to take care
of the baby yourself?

271
00:21:59,290 --> 00:22:00,400
For what?

272
00:22:04,440 --> 00:22:06,480
Originally, it's my own business.

273
00:22:07,480 --> 00:22:08,470
Now that I have made a decision,

274
00:22:08,560 --> 00:22:10,160
I'll be responsible for myself.

275
00:22:15,690 --> 00:22:16,690
Where's Hua?

276
00:22:17,450 --> 00:22:18,960
Why didn't she come with you?

277
00:22:23,320 --> 00:22:24,760
I didn't tell her.

278
00:22:25,080 --> 00:22:26,720
With her temper,

279
00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:29,640
I can't imagine what
she'd do after knowing about it.

280
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:33,480
What about the baby?

281
00:22:35,610 --> 00:22:37,160
What are you going to do in the future?

282
00:22:56,360 --> 00:22:58,320
What did you do early in the morning?
You didn't answer the phone.

283
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:02,800
She came to look for me.

284
00:23:05,120 --> 00:23:06,440
Why don't you invite me in?

285
00:23:19,520 --> 00:23:21,080
It's a nice house.

286
00:23:21,170 --> 00:23:22,280
You are rich.

287
00:23:22,720 --> 00:23:24,750
This is the house
of the counsellor's relative.

288
00:23:24,840 --> 00:23:25,920
It's much cheaper.

289
00:23:26,450 --> 00:23:27,330
Good.

290
00:23:31,960 --> 00:23:33,280
I just came to have a look.

291
00:23:33,370 --> 00:23:34,720
I'm leaving now if it's all right.

292
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:36,160
Now that you're here,

293
00:23:36,600 --> 00:23:38,080
why don't you leave after eating?

294
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:46,130
The last one.

295
00:23:47,280 --> 00:23:48,510
You cooked all the dishes yourself?

296
00:23:48,600 --> 00:23:49,480
Yes.

297
00:23:49,890 --> 00:23:50,880
You're great!

298
00:23:51,480 --> 00:23:52,600
Then I can set my mind at rest.

299
00:23:53,360 --> 00:23:54,680
Let me have a taste of your cuisine.

300
00:24:25,040 --> 00:24:26,590
What were you doing in the morning?

301
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:28,440
I've been waiting for you all morning.

302
00:24:29,490 --> 00:24:30,870
I met a friend.

303
00:24:30,960 --> 00:24:32,760
Which is more important, friends or job?

304
00:24:34,680 --> 00:24:35,880
You should go once more tomorrow.

305
00:24:37,280 --> 00:24:38,520
Okay, I see.

306
00:24:56,130 --> 00:24:57,330
Have you decided yet?

307
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:03,880
I don't know.

308
00:25:04,600 --> 00:25:05,990
You have to make up your mind soon.

309
00:25:06,080 --> 00:25:07,280
It can't be delayed.

310
00:25:08,960 --> 00:25:10,090
I know.

311
00:25:12,240 --> 00:25:13,400
Li Qing Tong.

312
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,840
What have you done in the bathroom?

313
00:25:14,930 --> 00:25:16,160
The toilet is so dirty.

314
00:25:17,690 --> 00:25:18,920
I've done nothing.

315
00:25:19,560 --> 00:25:21,150
I poured the leftovers in it.

316
00:25:21,240 --> 00:25:22,550
It was accidentally soiled.

317
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,200
Leftovers can't be poured in the toilet.

318
00:25:24,290 --> 00:25:25,310
It will get clogged.

319
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,520
Do you have any common sense?

320
00:25:32,770 --> 00:25:34,600
I feel like I can't hide it anymore.

321
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:43,240
I have to find a new house.

322
00:25:44,210 --> 00:25:46,150
At least there's a place
for me to think about

323
00:25:46,240 --> 00:25:47,960
what to do next.

324
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:52,150
Can you help me?

325
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:53,960
It's really inconvenient for me now.

326
00:25:56,850 --> 00:25:57,470
Okay.

327
00:25:57,560 --> 00:25:58,440
Leave it to me.

328
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:03,840
You're asking me to move out?

329
00:26:04,520 --> 00:26:06,880
I told you my uncle would come
and stay for a period of time.

330
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:08,550
You can't stand him.

331
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:10,400
Why?

332
00:26:11,080 --> 00:26:12,190
He grinds his teeth in sleep,

333
00:26:12,280 --> 00:26:14,040
farts and snores.

334
00:26:14,130 --> 00:26:16,510
By the way,
my uncle is a sleepwalker.

335
00:26:16,600 --> 00:26:20,480
I don't know whether he goes to your room
and does something at night.

336
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:23,640
Where will I live?

337
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:26,200
Anywhere.

338
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:28,510
You're going to the South anyway.

339
00:26:28,600 --> 00:26:31,240
It doesn't matter whether
you live in the house or not.

340
00:26:33,520 --> 00:26:35,080
Fine.

341
00:26:37,040 --> 00:26:38,720
You don't want me to go with you?

342
00:26:39,770 --> 00:26:43,230
No. They said this time family members
are not allowed to accompany the interns.

343
00:26:43,320 --> 00:26:44,440
She has to go herself.

344
00:26:45,760 --> 00:26:46,840
What rule is this?

345
00:26:47,250 --> 00:26:48,690
Does teaching require to be separated?

346
00:26:48,840 --> 00:26:49,920
All right.

347
00:26:50,010 --> 00:26:51,880
It's all for good treatment.

348
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:53,720
Before finding a proper job,

349
00:26:54,120 --> 00:26:55,550
staying home is still staying home.

350
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:57,370
Hurry up. Don't be late.

351
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:12,040
Don't listen to them.

352
00:27:12,130 --> 00:27:13,680
Call me when you get there.

353
00:27:13,770 --> 00:27:14,960
I'll go to see you secretly.

354
00:27:46,570 --> 00:27:47,720
You are gone.

355
00:27:48,600 --> 00:27:50,760
What's the point of staying here alone?

356
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:18,370
What place is this?

357
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:21,600
It's the house for Da Fan and I rent.

358
00:28:21,920 --> 00:28:22,680
He has moved out..

359
00:28:22,770 --> 00:28:24,160
So there's a room for you.

360
00:28:27,170 --> 00:28:28,050
What's the matter?

361
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:30,280
You also live here?

362
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:33,790
Don't worry.

363
00:28:33,880 --> 00:28:34,880
You can live here at ease.

364
00:28:34,970 --> 00:28:36,160
I won't bother you.

365
00:28:38,560 --> 00:28:39,280
Okay.

366
00:28:39,370 --> 00:28:40,510
Have a seat.

367
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:42,280
I'll clean the room for you.

368
00:28:58,720 --> 00:28:59,730
Li Qing Tong.

369
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:04,240
I'll put tomorrow's breakfast
in the living room.

370
00:29:04,320 --> 00:29:05,960
Remember to eat after getting up.

371
00:29:44,240 --> 00:29:45,200
Hua.

372
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:47,990
I'm fine here.

373
00:29:48,080 --> 00:29:50,480
Li Qing Tong.
What do you want to eat tomorrow morning?

374
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:54,600
Then I'll put the breakfast
in the living room.

375
00:30:09,170 --> 00:30:10,160
Li Qing Tong.

376
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:11,960
Remember to have breakfast
after getting up tomorrow.

377
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:29,680
Li Qing Tong, remember to have breakfast.

378
00:30:31,760 --> 00:30:32,640
Well...

379
00:30:33,040 --> 00:30:33,920
Thank you.

380
00:30:36,840 --> 00:30:37,720
It's okay.

381
00:30:39,530 --> 00:30:41,000
Remember to have breakfast.

382
00:31:19,840 --> 00:31:20,760
Hello.

383
00:31:32,040 --> 00:31:32,920
[Li Qing Tong.]

384
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:35,240
[Li Qing Tong, wake up.]

385
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:37,230
What's wrong?

386
00:31:37,320 --> 00:31:38,280
[Wake up.]

387
00:31:38,360 --> 00:31:39,720
Something happened to your family.

388
00:31:41,210 --> 00:31:45,490
[Tieyuan People's Hospital]

389
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:54,080
Mum.

390
00:31:56,330 --> 00:31:57,210
Tong.

391
00:31:58,040 --> 00:31:59,410
Tong.

392
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:03,050
Where's Dad?

393
00:32:04,520 --> 00:32:06,010
Where's Dad?

394
00:32:43,280 --> 00:32:44,360
You're here.

395
00:32:48,120 --> 00:32:49,000
Dad.

396
00:32:52,960 --> 00:32:54,150
Hua is here, too.

397
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:55,360
Uncle.

398
00:32:56,880 --> 00:32:58,240
I have never seen this guy.

399
00:32:58,680 --> 00:32:59,720
What's your name?

400
00:32:59,800 --> 00:33:01,840
Hello, Uncle, I'm Chen Jun He.

401
00:33:03,360 --> 00:33:04,240
This...

402
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:06,950
We used to be in the same school.

403
00:33:07,040 --> 00:33:08,270
We were classmates.

404
00:33:08,360 --> 00:33:09,730
Yes, classmates.

405
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:12,320
I almost misunderstood it.

406
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,400
This boy is...

407
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:16,330
really good-looking.

408
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,080
Well.

409
00:33:20,240 --> 00:33:21,360
It's all your mother's fault.

410
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:23,600
I've told her. Right?

411
00:33:23,690 --> 00:33:24,830
The children have just graduated.

412
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:26,130
They're looking for a job.

413
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:28,000
Why did you call them back?

414
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:29,590
It's not a big deal.

415
00:33:29,680 --> 00:33:30,680
I'm fine.

416
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:31,800
I'm...

417
00:33:32,360 --> 00:33:33,440
I'm fine now.

418
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:36,360
Qing Tong.

419
00:33:36,440 --> 00:33:37,270
Qing Tong.

420
00:33:37,360 --> 00:33:38,720
Look.

421
00:33:39,120 --> 00:33:41,090
Isn't it the style from those years?

422
00:33:42,520 --> 00:33:43,920
I'm really handsome.

423
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:47,280
No?

424
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:53,160
I've gotten ready.

425
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:54,560
Look.

426
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:55,560
Come on.

427
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:56,600
Feng Xia.

428
00:33:56,760 --> 00:33:58,160
Come here. Come here, Qing Tong.

429
00:33:58,250 --> 00:33:59,400
Let's take a picture.

430
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:01,900
We haven't taken a picture
of the whole family in a long time.

431
00:34:01,990 --> 00:34:02,870
Come on.

432
00:34:02,950 --> 00:34:03,640
Come on.

433
00:34:03,720 --> 00:34:04,600
Well.

434
00:34:04,760 --> 00:34:05,350
Uncle, I'll take it for you.

435
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:06,310
Okay, come here.

436
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:07,280
Come here.

437
00:34:12,239 --> 00:34:13,120
Come here.

438
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:14,070
Come on.

439
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:18,719
Three, two.

440
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,679
Don't cry. Don't cry.

441
00:34:24,120 --> 00:34:25,000
Three.

442
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:26,239
Two.

443
00:34:32,719 --> 00:34:35,239
Your mother is too emotional.

444
00:34:40,239 --> 00:34:41,750
Don't cry, Qing Tong. Don't cry.

445
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:43,600
Take a good picture with me.

446
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:46,920
Three, two, one.

447
00:34:49,440 --> 00:34:50,320
Okay?

448
00:34:53,719 --> 00:34:55,440
Sit down, sit down.

449
00:35:05,120 --> 00:35:06,000
I'm a little tired.

450
00:35:14,690 --> 00:35:16,710
[Tieyuan People's Hospital]

451
00:35:24,600 --> 00:35:25,680
What did the doctor say?

452
00:35:27,960 --> 00:35:28,920
Advanced lung cancer.

453
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:31,920
Maybe, there are only a few days left.

454
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:49,360
Your hands are the same

455
00:35:50,720 --> 00:35:52,440
as they were when you were a kid.

456
00:35:54,720 --> 00:35:56,120
They're soft.

457
00:35:56,680 --> 00:35:58,080
They're warm.

458
00:35:59,560 --> 00:36:01,080
Do you remember

459
00:36:01,720 --> 00:36:03,250
you were holding my hands tight

460
00:36:03,720 --> 00:36:05,240
when you were a kid?

461
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:06,880
Do you remember?

462
00:36:09,240 --> 00:36:11,610
Why didn't you tell me?

463
00:36:14,080 --> 00:36:15,920
That's what you've been like in the past.

464
00:36:16,600 --> 00:36:17,800
You didn't tell me you were laid off.

465
00:36:17,890 --> 00:36:19,230
You didn't tell me you were sick.

466
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:21,320
Don't you regard me as
a member of the family?

467
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:24,880
How do you know I was laid off?

468
00:36:27,890 --> 00:36:28,830
I knew that a long time ago.

469
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:30,040
I knew it in my last year of high school.

470
00:36:42,850 --> 00:36:44,120
You're definitely my daughter.

471
00:36:44,520 --> 00:36:46,320
My daughter is smart.

472
00:36:47,040 --> 00:36:48,370
I thought

473
00:36:49,010 --> 00:36:50,890
I could keep it from you.

474
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:54,200
So

475
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,360
it's the reason why

476
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:57,520
you chose the college

477
00:36:59,120 --> 00:37:00,690
that doesn't charge, right?

478
00:37:03,800 --> 00:37:05,720
Or I'd be the way you guys
think I would be.

479
00:37:06,040 --> 00:37:07,870
I'm like a fool, I can do nothing.

480
00:37:07,960 --> 00:37:09,110
You two have to bear all the burden.

481
00:37:09,200 --> 00:37:10,480
Only you two.

482
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:13,800
Qing Tong.

483
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:16,360
You're wrong.

484
00:37:18,170 --> 00:37:19,930
It's because your mum and I

485
00:37:21,110 --> 00:37:22,950
knew

486
00:37:24,160 --> 00:37:25,960
you could bear

487
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:28,680
all the burden.

488
00:37:29,560 --> 00:37:31,640
That's why we didn't tell you.

489
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:36,480
I've been

490
00:37:38,530 --> 00:37:40,760
useless all my life.

491
00:37:43,240 --> 00:37:44,320
But

492
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:47,080
my happiest thing

493
00:37:48,560 --> 00:37:50,280
was marrying your mother.

494
00:37:52,040 --> 00:37:53,800
Even happier

495
00:37:54,490 --> 00:37:56,440
when you mother gave birth to you.

496
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:07,040
What a pity!

497
00:38:10,280 --> 00:38:11,480
What a pity!

498
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:16,680
Dad.

499
00:38:21,040 --> 00:38:22,360
What a pity!

500
00:38:24,720 --> 00:38:26,080
Dad.

501
00:38:28,120 --> 00:38:29,520
Dad.

502
00:38:30,200 --> 00:38:31,720
What a pity.

503
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:30,160
Hua.

504
00:39:30,560 --> 00:39:33,040
I have to tell you something.

505
00:39:51,600 --> 00:39:52,480
Where's Auntie?

506
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:56,730
She went to prepare
the funeral affairs of Uncle.

507
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:03,360
What can I do?

508
00:40:03,450 --> 00:40:04,720
Just ask for it.

509
00:40:11,640 --> 00:40:12,640
You also know about it?

510
00:40:15,800 --> 00:40:16,960
About the baby.

511
00:40:22,240 --> 00:40:23,280
Do you know

512
00:40:24,130 --> 00:40:26,480
that she's decided
to give birth to the baby?

513
00:40:58,840 --> 00:40:59,800
Are you sure?

514
00:41:07,280 --> 00:41:09,040
Have you thought about
what to do with the baby?

515
00:41:10,130 --> 00:41:11,280
You'll be a single mother.

516
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:13,760
The child will have
no household registration.

517
00:41:14,320 --> 00:41:15,470
How will the child live in the future?

518
00:41:15,560 --> 00:41:16,520
How will the child go to school?

519
00:41:22,770 --> 00:41:23,840
Li Qing Tong.

520
00:41:24,920 --> 00:41:26,640
But the baby is mine.

521
00:41:30,120 --> 00:41:32,640
It's a life.

522
00:41:33,680 --> 00:41:35,600
The child is my family.

523
00:41:37,240 --> 00:41:39,840
I can already feel the baby.

524
00:41:43,160 --> 00:41:45,480
I don't want to lose
another family member.

525
00:41:56,450 --> 00:41:57,330
Li Qing Tong.

526
00:41:58,720 --> 00:41:59,970
Have you decided?

527
00:42:13,800 --> 00:42:16,370
[Li Qing Tong is pregnant,
and Wu Zhi Xun is the baby's father.]

528
00:42:17,520 --> 00:42:19,240
[Will I be there in the future?]

529
00:42:32,330 --> 00:42:33,920
[Maybe it's destiny.]

530
00:42:34,240 --> 00:42:35,800
[Even if I give up myself]

531
00:42:36,170 --> 00:42:37,630
[I can't take Li Qing Tong
out of her life]

532
00:42:37,720 --> 00:42:40,040
[dragged down by love and the child.]

533
00:42:42,200 --> 00:42:43,720
[Will the baby be me?]

534
00:42:44,240 --> 00:42:45,120
[I don't know.]

535
00:42:45,360 --> 00:42:46,480
[I don't care.]

536
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:49,160
[I just want to spend more time
with her now.]

537
00:42:49,600 --> 00:42:51,240
[Even if it's just for one day.]

538
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:52,600
[I'm going to stay with her for one day.]

539
00:43:09,700 --> 00:43:10,120
[Household Register]

540
00:43:10,120 --> 00:43:11,880
[But I didn't expect]

541
00:43:12,200 --> 00:43:13,630
[I wouldn't be the only one]

542
00:43:13,720 --> 00:43:15,160
[willing to keep her company.]

543
00:43:28,000 --> 00:43:29,880
Household register, flowers and nine yuan.

544
00:43:30,320 --> 00:43:31,410
Let's get married.

545
00:43:41,880 --> 00:43:43,410
Chen Jun He,
is there something wrong with you?

546
00:43:44,290 --> 00:43:45,280
It's none of your business.

547
00:43:45,360 --> 00:43:46,430
Why will you get married with me?

548
00:43:46,520 --> 00:43:47,960
What do you want?

549
00:43:49,360 --> 00:43:50,280
I want nothing.

550
00:43:51,080 --> 00:43:52,230
But I want the baby to have
a registered permanent residence

551
00:43:52,320 --> 00:43:54,120
a name, an identity and a father.

552
00:43:54,620 --> 00:43:55,470
That's all.

553
00:43:55,560 --> 00:43:56,680
No way.

554
00:43:58,320 --> 00:43:59,800
I don't want to owe you anything.

555
00:44:00,280 --> 00:44:01,330
You don't owe me.

556
00:44:02,280 --> 00:44:03,160
But the baby does.

557
00:44:04,320 --> 00:44:05,880
So after the child is born

558
00:44:06,400 --> 00:44:07,360
you ask the child to make a kowtow

559
00:44:07,960 --> 00:44:08,840
and call me dad.

560
00:44:09,880 --> 00:44:11,130
We're even.

561
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:17,110
Li Qing Tong.

562
00:44:17,200 --> 00:44:18,230
Adults' things

563
00:44:18,320 --> 00:44:19,760
have nothing to do with the baby.

564
00:44:20,760 --> 00:44:22,070
You can't have this baby born

565
00:44:22,160 --> 00:44:23,480
feeling inferior to others.

566
00:44:24,560 --> 00:44:26,090
I have experienced it.

567
00:44:26,480 --> 00:44:27,760
I know it's hard.

568
00:44:27,850 --> 00:44:29,680
So can you think about it for your baby?

569
00:44:33,840 --> 00:44:34,760
You must get a marriage certificate

570
00:44:35,920 --> 00:44:36,920
with me today.

571
00:44:37,920 --> 00:44:39,680
I want the baby to be born

572
00:44:40,120 --> 00:44:41,400
and have an identity successfully.

573
00:44:46,280 --> 00:44:47,520
Then we'll end the relationship.

574
00:44:50,410 --> 00:44:51,850
Take it as if you owe me.

575
00:44:54,520 --> 00:44:55,880
Repay me in the next life.
